{"tid":2163936,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國參議院發表通俄門最終調查報告 指普京直接指揮駭客攻擊民主黨並協助川普贏得2016年大選","createTime":"2020-08-19T03:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T11:30:42.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e0532623857e818b344a769f4129db6204969ca2","tid":2163936,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T03:00:20.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普「通俄門」爭議近期又有新進展；美國參議院情報委員會（Senate Select Committee on Intelligence）在昨日發布一份「通俄門」最終調查報告，該報告多達966頁，稱俄羅斯利用川普的前競選經理馬那佛特（Paul Manafort）和維基解密網站，協助川普贏得2016年大選，且稱發現俄羅斯總理普廷甚至直接指揮對民主黨的駭客攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》評論該報告，認為它可能是關於2016年美國總統大選爭議中的最權威公開報告；報告指出，維基解密在俄羅斯協助川普對希拉蕊克林頓（Hillary Clinton）選戰中發揮關鍵作用，且該網站可能明白自己正在協助俄羅斯情報機構。報告又指，發現俄羅斯總理普廷親自指揮對民主黨的網路、帳號發動駭客攻擊，並洩露對希拉蕊不利的資訊。<br />\n<br />\n2018年11月時，馬那佛特被爆出曾在2013、2015及2016年，於厄瓜多駐倫敦大使館密會維基解密創始人朱利安阿桑奇（Julian Assange）<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n針對馬那佛特，情報委員會聲稱，馬那佛特在2016年選舉期間及前後，都和俄國寡頭財團大亨歐柏嘉（Oleg Deripaska）以及「俄羅斯情報官員」基利姆尼克（Konstantin Kilimnik）勾結；委員會發現<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n對此，馬那佛特律師並未給予評論，維基解密也尚未回應。川普競選團隊發言人墨托（Tim Murtaugh）則在昨日回應指出，該報告證實川普在2016年的選戰中與俄羅斯之間並無「勾結」，並將此爭議稱作「騙局」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3264626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3264626&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5so9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=415f0485\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3264626&h=7c7bb401\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3264626</a>"},{"pid":"de9eae7b59f5c08efeb32830848007abdd34cdca","tid":2163936,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T03:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf98447cfe488e0493f42aeff64fa2e595159e1","tid":2163936,"uid":362135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T03:14:40.000Z","msg":"俄仔為正義而戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eab786048726dff9ab9d5d6f0fa7e91a7d0e6f8","tid":2163936,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T11:27:46.000Z","msg":"支持俄仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62769ffba2861c1ee965305005d4ff0f0667164","tid":2163936,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T11:30:42.000Z","msg":"首先要搞清楚<br />\n俄佬介入選舉，同侵勾結俄佬係兩件事<br />\n民主黨指控侵通俄，係同俄佬勾結<br />\n如果件事係假，即係民主黨政府用行政權力入鳩侵<br />\n咁就係另一個層級既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}